{"tid":289494,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"“ 我係中国人，我唔會去韓國 “","createTime":"2017-06-19T05:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T05:01:42.000Z","uid":36157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15ece7cc388dcd0c871b4ff5600274a7fe704c25","tid":289494,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"5分鐘前，係日本城入面，兩個香港話怪怪地既阿姐。<br />\n<br />\n姐A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐B <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有朋友叫我去西藏玩，我唔去。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 韓國仲好啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係中国人，我唔去韓國！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係日本你都唔去啦？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係中国人，唔去！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望中国人都淨係去中国就好了。"}]}